isentangled, generalizable features even with few samples. The significance of this work lies in bridging low-level visual patterns with high-level semantics in a self-supervised manner, enabling more intelligent and context-aware knowledge transfer. It offers a paradigm shift from blind feature copying to semantically informed distillation, potentially improving performance across various long-tailed vision tasks such as fine-grained classification, medical imaging, and autonomous driving perception systems.",
